# m5_dismember.shot — P12 damage feedback layers.
#
# Verifies the four runtime layers landed at P12:
#   1. hit-flash white-additive tint (~80–120 ms after damage)
#   2. persistent decal placeholder dots — one per damage event, 16-deep
#      ring per visible part — accumulating on the limbs that took fire
#   3. heavy initial blood spray + pinned FX_STUMP emitter on dismember
#   4. fx_spawn_smoke from limbs at < 30% HP (visible BEFORE the dummy
#      dies, since leg dismemberment isn't lethal — only head detach is)
#
# Stump-cap SPRITES require a chassis atlas, which doesn't ship at P12
# (asset gen lands at P15/P16). The spec calls out "capsule fallback:
# stump caps don't render"; the heavy initial blood spray + pinned
# emitter sell the dismemberment without it.
#
# Strategy: aim at the dummy's left knee. Each Pulse Rifle hit deals
# 12.6 dmg (knee multiplier 0.7) so:
#   5 hits  → limb HP 80 → 17 → smoke threshold engaged (frac 0.21)
#   7 hits  → limb HP   ≤  -8  → DISMEMBER L_LEG (non-lethal, dummy alive)
# Dummy chassis HP starts at 150; 7 shots × 18 base = 126 dmg → 24 HP
# alive at end of fire window. Window for "alive with missing leg +
# smoke trail" is ticks ~50-120.
#
# Run:
#   ./soldut --shot tests/shots/m5_dismember.shot
# Output:
#   build/shots/m5_dismember/{t010_pristine,t022_first_flash,...}.png
#   build/shots/m5_dismember/sheet.png

window 1280 720
seed   12 12
out    build/shots/m5_dismember
loadout - "Pulse Rifle" Sidearm Light Standard
contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 480 270

# Both player and dummy stand on the right-side platform (cols 70–79
# in level_build_tutorial, x range 2240–2560, top y=1024). Player at
# x=2280 sits 120 px left of the dummy at x=2400 on the same row 32
# surface. World-space `aim` (not `mouse`) so the rifle target stays
# locked on the dummy's left knee regardless of camera follow.
spawn_at 2280 984
aim      2400 1005

# Pristine reference — dummy untouched.
at  10 shot t010_pristine

# Fire the Pulse Rifle for ~50 ticks: ≈7 shots at 110 ms cycle. Each
# 12.6-dmg knee hit accumulates on L_LEG limb HP and on the leg-upper /
# leg-lower decal rings. Hit-flash kicks at every shot to f=1.0 and
# decays over 6 ticks.
at  20 press fire
at  70 release fire

# Capture mid-flash on the first shot (flash f ≈ 0.7 at t=22).
at  22 shot t022_first_flash

# Mid-fight: decals visible on the leg sprite area, multiple flashes
# stacked through the cycle.
at  40 shot t040_decals

# Smoke begins firing once a limb is below 30% HP (~5 hits in).
at  60 shot t060_smoke_begins

# Dismember moment (~tick 60-65 if all 7 hits land on the leg). Heavy
# initial spray + FX_STUMP emitter pinned to the parent particle.
at  78 shot t078_spray

# Pinned emitter still dripping for ~1.5 s after dismember; smoke
# trailing the gibbed limb (it's still in the particle pool, frac=0).
at 130 shot t130_emitter

# Settled state — body has stopped, blood pooled, smoke continuing.
at 220 shot t220_settled

at 280 end
